c: 12
v: 78
t: "Kay tooboko nacror kaat (Nabii Yuusuf kinnuk) gurrusak sinni abbah heen xagana duudusaanakeh, konnaba le qaziizow ! usuk (binyaamiin kinnuk) kaxxa idaltuh yan abbay kaak baxsimam duude waa lek kay aftok nek numuk teyna bet, nanu diggah neh abteh tan maqaaneh meqe marih numuh koo nablek kaak iyyen"